\begin_inset Formula $\succeq$
\end_inset

 is monotone if 
\begin_inset Formula $x\succ y$
\end_inset

 for any 
\begin_inset Formula $x,y\in X$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{l}>y_{l}$
\end_inset

 for all commodities 
\begin_inset Formula $l$
\end_inset

.
